        <h1 class="page-title">Split Button</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">
          The Split Button is a compound action component that combines a primary action button with a secondary dropdown trigger (chevron). It allows users to execute a default action with one click, while also providing access to additional related actions via the dropdown chevron.
