                <tr><td><code>Tab</code> or <code>Arrow Right</code></td><td>Move focus from the button part to the chevron part.</td></tr>
                <tr><td><code>Enter</code> / <code>Space</code> (on chevron)</td><td>Open the dropdown menu.</td></tr>
