            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li>The chevron/dropdown trigger must include <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">aria-haspopup="menu"</code> to indicate it controls a menu.</li>
